lenders.name: Julie
lenders.loan_because: Tumml is an urban ventures accelerator with the mission of empowering entrepreneurs to solve urban problems.  We choose borrowers that have participated in Tumml's accelerator program, meaning that we have spent four months working day by day alongside the entrepreneur.  Each borrower is someone we trust and believe is making an outsized impact on our urban communities.

lenders.name: Nilima
lenders.loan_because: Any SME or venture that's creating a better world or an entrepreneur that seems truly dedicated to her/his pursuit!

lenders.name: Dan
lenders.loan_because: People that seem in more need of help than others. Unique business, perhaps helping "an underdog".

lenders.name: Mikhal
lenders.loan_because: It's tough to choose among so many inspiring entrepreneurs! However, if I've read about their story somewhere, or it resonates with me personally (i.e. a mother, or they come from a part of the world I've traveled to or dream about ), it tends to catch my eye.
